classitems.name: ajax
classitems.examples:
$.ajax({
  url: "requestHandler.php",
  success: function (data, xhr) {
    console.log(data, xhr);
  },
  method: "GET"
});

classitems.name: get
example:
$.get({
  url: "path/to/file.js",
  success: function (data) {
    console.log(data);
  }
}); // Longer form, the below is preferred

$.get("path/to/file.js", function (data) {
  console.log(data);
}); // This does the exact same function as above

$.get("path/to/file.js", function (data) {
  console.log(data);
}, {
  error: function (err) {
    console.error(err);
  }
}); // Shortform, with more options

classitems.name: post
example:
$.post({
  url: "path/to/file.js",
  success: function (data) {
    console.log(data);
  },
  data: JSON.encode(obj)
}); // Longer form, the below is preferred

$.post("path/to/file.js", function (data) {
  console.log(data);
}, {
  data: JSON.encode(obj),
  error: function (err) {
    console.error(err);
  }
}); // Shortform, with more options
